  <!-- Síntesis de la actividad -->
  <paragraphs>
    <title><custom ref="synthesis-actividad-titulo"/></title>
    <p>[+++++++++++++++]</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Invite students to share their work for completing each algorithm.</li>
      <li>
        <q>¿Qué hicieron de una forma diferente al completar cada uno de estos problemas?</q>  (With Andre’s work I subtracted all the place values, then I had to add up all the parts of the difference. With Clare’s work once I subtracted the digits in each place value, the answer was complete.)
      </li>
    </ul>
  </paragraphs>


